  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/4dc4559d4929af23d9fa9fbed54ec946.poster.avif?t=1763327738\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/4dc4559d4929af23d9fa9fbed54ec946.webm?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/4dc4559d4929af23d9fa9fbed54ec946.mp4?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Siobhan awakens from a dream at the highest point of the island Rashinmore. Rashinmore was once a quiet and warm community, games were played and friends were made. Nothing bad would ever happen here, but things change. In the last week a disappearance has left people lost and devastated. Everyone wants answers, but the ones in charge don't seem to have a clue. If they're not going to lift a finger to find out whats going on, who will...? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Things feel different when the sun goes down... is there something hiding in the dark?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/b86866095ecc1fbd6a21922ae687a762.poster.avif?t=1763327738\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/b86866095ecc1fbd6a21922ae687a762.webm?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/b86866095ecc1fbd6a21922ae687a762.mp4?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An Aisling is an adventure game focused on exploration, story, and character. Make friends or enemies as you try to uncover why people are dissappearing on the island of Rashinmore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/fb1f7bd32f59e9665217a37551affce1.poster.avif?t=1763327738\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/fb1f7bd32f59e9665217a37551affce1.webm?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/fb1f7bd32f59e9665217a37551affce1.mp4?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump, talk or even punch your way through the island as you uncover the mystery on Rashinmore.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose to make friends or enemies with a colourful cast of characters and creatures. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Paint pictures, catch creatures, conduct choirs, run races and see stars.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Original art and soundtrack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Not one but two dogs! There's maybe even a secret third... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/5f8efaea04d0adedcfca6f6671a0f846.poster.avif?t=1763327738\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/5f8efaea04d0adedcfca6f6671a0f846.webm?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/5f8efaea04d0adedcfca6f6671a0f846.mp4?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/4dc4559d4929af23d9fa9fbed54ec946.poster.avif?t=1763327738\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/4dc4559d4929af23d9fa9fbed54ec946.webm?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/4dc4559d4929af23d9fa9fbed54ec946.mp4?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Siobhan awakens from a dream at the highest point of the island Rashinmore. Rashinmore was once a quiet and warm community, games were played and friends were made. Nothing bad would ever happen here, but things change. In the last week a disappearance has left people lost and devastated. Everyone wants answers, but the ones in charge don't seem to have a clue. If they're not going to lift a finger to find out whats going on, who will...? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Things feel different when the sun goes down... is there something hiding in the dark?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/b86866095ecc1fbd6a21922ae687a762.poster.avif?t=1763327738\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/b86866095ecc1fbd6a21922ae687a762.webm?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/b86866095ecc1fbd6a21922ae687a762.mp4?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An Aisling is an adventure game focused on exploration, story, and character. Make friends or enemies as you try to uncover why people are dissappearing on the island of Rashinmore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/fb1f7bd32f59e9665217a37551affce1.poster.avif?t=1763327738\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/fb1f7bd32f59e9665217a37551affce1.webm?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/fb1f7bd32f59e9665217a37551affce1.mp4?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump, talk or even punch your way through the island as you uncover the mystery on Rashinmore.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose to make friends or enemies with a colourful cast of characters and creatures. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Paint pictures, catch creatures, conduct choirs, run races and see stars.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Original art and soundtrack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Not one but two dogs! There's maybe even a secret third... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/5f8efaea04d0adedcfca6f6671a0f846.poster.avif?t=1763327738\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/5f8efaea04d0adedcfca6f6671a0f846.webm?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2663840/extras/5f8efaea04d0adedcfca6f6671a0f846.mp4?t=1763327738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
